Package: rbi.helpers
Version: 0.2
Date: 2016-11-04
Title: RBi Helper Functions
Author: Sebastian Funk <sebastian.funk@lshtm.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Sebastian Funk <sebastian.funk@lshtm.ac.uk>
Depends:
    rbi,
    data.table
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    lubridate,
    scales,
    coda,
    GGally,
    reshape2
Suggests:
    R.rsp
Description: Contains a collection of helper functions to use with rbi, the R interface to LibBi. It contains functions to adapt the proposal distribution and number of particles in particle Markov-Chain Monte Carlo, as well as a function to plot the outcomes of LibBi runs.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/sbfnk/RBi.helpers
